00:05:21.519 --> 00:05:30.519
Tyndale is often renowned for his influence on the English language, but his work was more than that of just scholarly ambition.

00:05:30.519 --> 00:05:37.519
Tyndale loved the Bible. Maybe it can be said of him that he shared the feelings of the Samist,

